### TypeScript — scroll listener

In your header component or app component:

  isScrolled = false;
  private scrollThreshold = 60;

  @HostListener('window:scroll')
  onWindowScroll(): void {
    this.isScrolled = window.scrollY > this.scrollThreshold;
  }

That's it. No requestAnimationFrame needed — the CSS transition 
handles the smoothness.

